20 shall be filed in Franklin Circuit Court or the Circuit Court of the county in which
21 the certificate holder was employed when the incident occurred in accordance with
22 KRS Chapter 13B which provides that all final orders of an agency shall be subject
23 to judicial review.
24 Section 2. KRS 156.095 is amended to read as follows:
25 (1) (a) The Kentucky Department of Education shall establish, direct, and maintain a
26 statewide program of professional development to improve instruction in the
27 public schools.
