3 national and state criminal background check by the Department
4 of Kentucky State Police and the Federal Bureau of Investigation
5 through an accredited teacher education institution in which the
6 student teacher is enrolled and who have a clear CA/N check.
7 2. The Education Professional Standards Board may promulgate
8 administrative regulations to impose additional qualifications to meet
